<!--<h4>First Face.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="1"/><unclear>sva</unclear>sti śrīmatu cāḷukyacakravartti
<lb n="2"/><unclear>ja</unclear>gadēkamalladēvavarṣa
<lb n="3"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> ya siddhārttisaṁvatsarada
<lb n="4"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> da puṇnami sōmavāra vi
<lb n="5" break="no"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> ta Uttarāyaṇa saṁ
<lb n="6" break="no"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> ṇa nimittavāgi tārkkikacū
<lb n="7" break="no"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> <unclear>ma</unclear>ṇi kēsavapaṁṇḍitaru mādha
<lb n="8" break="no"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> <unclear>paṁ</unclear>ḍitaru śrīmaduttamadagrahā
<lb n="9" break="no"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> takanahaḷḷiya mallikārjju
<lb n="10" break="no"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> ra Aṁgabhōgaraṁgabōgajīrṇnō
<lb n="11" break="no"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> haḍagile haṁnnera
<lb n="12" break="no"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> ḷibāḍaṁ kaṁgoḍa teṁ
<lb n="13" break="no"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> holadoḷage Ādityaghaisā
<lb n="14" break="no"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> lu <unclear>nidhiya</unclear> pageyi
<lb n="15"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> ru <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
</p>

<!--<h4>Second Face.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="16"/>ntu nūṟu mattaru keyi sarvvanama
<lb n="17" break="no"/>syavāgi Ādityaghaisāsara kaiyya
<lb n="18" break="no"/>lu moṟageya mallikārjjunadēvargge<unclear>dhā</unclear>
<lb n="19" break="no"/><unclear>rā</unclear>pūrbbakaṁ māḍi biṭṭaru I darmmavaṁ ya
<lb n="20" break="no"/>vanāgiyuṁ kiḍisidavaru vāra
<lb n="21" break="no"/>ṇāsiyalu sāyirakavileyaṁ konda pā
<lb n="22" break="no"/>takkamakku <g type="ddanda">.</g> © svadattaṁ paradattaṁ vā
<lb n="23"/>yō harēti vasuṁdharā saṣṭirvvari
<lb n="24" break="no"/>ṣasahasrāṇi miṣṭāyāṁ jāya
<lb n="25" break="no"/>tē krimi sasanamidāudelliya sa
<lb n="26" break="no"/>sana Āritarēke salisuve nānī sasa<supplied reason="omitted">na</supplied>va
<lb n="27" break="no"/>neṁba pātakana sakaḷaṁ rauravake gaḷagaḷani
<lb n="28" break="no"/>ḷiva <g type="ddanda">.</g> ©
</p>

